snippet.title: Far - Out : Selene | Official Trailer 2017
snippet.description:
Xbox Version:
https://www.microsoft.com/p/far-out/9p29m8mz7zmf
PC Version:
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/far-out

Far-Out is a hardcore survival adventure with dynamically changing gameplay and multiple endings. Made with the old-school quests such as The Dig, Space Quest, Full Throttle, Another World and Blade Runner in mind.

Developed by Alexander Sergejeff
Music by Michael Donner
Cast:  Nic Mepham
